# Weighted risk score (0–100)

Implemented in `src/engine/risk-scorer.ts`. **Higher = greater compliance urgency.**

| Component | Max pts | Calculation |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| FSA rating pressure | 40 | `((5 - clamp(rating,0,5)) / 5) × 40`; unrated → 20 |
| Inspection staleness | 35 | `min(daysSinceInspection / 730, 1) × 35` |
| Low-rating urgency | 15 | rating ≤1 → 15; rating 2 → 10; rating 3 → 5; else 0 |
| Contact gap | 10 | no phone **and** no website → 10; one missing → 5; else 0 |

**Total:** `round(sum)`, clamped to 0–100.

## Bands

| Band | Range |
|------|-------|
| Critical | 75–100 |
| High | 50–74 |
| Medium | 25–49 |
| Low | 0–24 |

Use bands for dashboard accent colors and outreach prioritization.
